The paper deals with the problem of measuring the similarity between two lattices, which is a fundamental problem in computational geometry and number theory. The paper uses tools from computational complexity, optimization, and algorithm design to study the problem. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.CC (Computational Complexity), cs.CG (Computational Geometry), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
